{"tid":906112,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我真係唔知自己人生係做緊咩","createTime":"2018-11-17T16:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T17:15:05.000Z","uid":163529,"like":77,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0230b13e4737c243f80e3d2db61a690df5eb367a","tid":906112,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T16:47:11.000Z","msg":"感覺一生都係活在失敗之中，<br />\n返緊份工又無前途，得閒就食飽訓<br />\n戶口又得四位數，結婚買樓都唔夠<br />\n屋企又係公屋，都唔敢結婚生仔<br />\n自己又未有目標，對每一樣野都無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到朋友個個都有成就，知道自己做緊咩<br />\n<br />\n我就真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：一個人飲緊啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db74ec0a918395569762e4c073b29b5d39ca288","tid":906112,"uid":208364,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"呢度都無人理你添"},{"pid":"ab55aa2b2722ea6b97785463b9f14964670d59a1","tid":906112,"uid":27793,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:06:58.000Z","msg":"第一要問你既係，你夢想係咩？你所希望既未來人生畫面係點？<br />\n<br />\n第二，你有無行動過？"},{"pid":"51144ac1691bb797e3578e70200885cd70fd7a0d","tid":906112,"uid":107408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"屌係咪講緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93ceaf35f82d1921164354fd9a4c96ed8c4fcba","tid":906112,"uid":168589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:14:04.000Z","msg":"窮人係咁嫁啦"},{"pid":"6af65c3334903ea242df4d6ba69b52fd9e50ef6e","tid":906112,"uid":59623,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"唔開心主要唔係窮，而係唔認命"},{"pid":"74892452cb7c145591fc23f17d5f9e255aa54dad","tid":906112,"uid":216760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"現況差不多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過大家加油<img src=